		<title lang="en"><![CDATA[Topic Preview - jQuery qTip2 Style Add-On for Precise Similar Topics]]></title>
		<description lang="en"><![CDATA[Uses jQuery and the qTip2 plug-in to create a nicer looking Topic Preview. These instructions add this feature to Precise Similar Topics installations.]]></description>
		<author-notes lang="en"><![CDATA[Use of these instructions requires that you have already installed:
-Precise Similar Topics (any version)
-Topic Preview
-Topic Preview for Precise Similar Topics add-on
-jQuery qTip2 style for Topic Preview add-on]]></author-notes>
